<refsect2><title><anchor id="GooCanvasItemModelSimple--line-dash"/>The &quot;<literal>line-dash</literal>&quot; property</title>
<indexterm><primary>GooCanvasItemModelSimple:line-dash</primary></indexterm><programlisting>  &quot;line-dash&quot;                <link linkend="GooCairoLineDash">GooCairoLineDash</link>      : Read / Write</programlisting>
